{
  "texts": [
    "A thorough analysis of the traits for classification and interpretation, however, is omitted in this work.",
    "Similarly, Mofrad et al. (2021) designed a framework for developing longitudinal MRI examination-based cognitive decline prediction models.",
    "Both the transition from ND to MCI and from MCI to AD is effectively detected through its utilization.",
    "The work focuses on developing a system that uses hippocampi morphometric measures taken by the MRI.",
    "The proposed approach demonstrates accuracy rates of 73% and 78% for detecting the transition from ND to MCI and from stable MCI to AD, respectively."
  ]
}